{
  "texts": [
    "During this process, we referred to the corresponding conversation logs and diary entries to ensure our interpretations were relevant to the contexts of the participants' interactions.",
    "Then, the three researchers discussed their initial codes and resolved discrepancies through regular meetings.",
    "In parallel, two researchers divided up the work to code the remaining data following the same procedure.",
    "During this process, We continuously compared the newly emerged code with the previous codes, which eventually led to a total of 693 codes.",
    "Next, the entire research team worked together to develop higher-level themes based on the initial codes."
  ]
}